metadata.name: Distant Universe Spart #1/50
metadata.description: In a distant universe, where dreams merge with reality, lies the mysterious NFT Spart collection. Inspired by the dreamlike and phantasmagorical works of the legendary Moebius, this collection transports its holders to a world where imagination is the keystone of existence. Each Holder will be offered a quality print and a freemint from the Geiko Collection.
